---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Culture | The Açai Club" description="Our story, our community. The Açai Club is more than bowls.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-28 pb-24 bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-light leading-[0.95]">
        More than<br /><span class="text-charcoal">just a bowl</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 text-grey text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
        The Açai Club started with a simple idea: bring the freshest açai bowls to the UK & build a community around healthy, active living.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section id="culture" class="py-24 bg-dark-surface">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-8">
            Born from the love of açai
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              It started with a trip abroad. Our founders discovered açai & got hooked. When they came back to the UK, nothing compared. So they made one from scratch in the kitchen, looked at each other & said: "We could sell this."
            </p>
            <p>
              They started from the back of their office. One fridge, one freezer, a few toppings, and a launch on delivery platforms. No store, no staff, just watching a baby cam pointed at the order machine from home.
            </p>
            <p>
              That grew into a store. Then another. Then another. And throughout it all, one thing never changed: the açai is never blended. 140g of pure açai, exactly as it comes. The way almost nobody else does it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/ig-about-1.webp" alt="Friends cheersing with açai bowls" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden mt-8"><img src="/images/ig-about-2.webp" alt="The Açai Club community out together on a Sunday morning" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden -mt-8"><img src="/images/ig-about-3.webp" alt="Pilates class fuelled by açai" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl aspect-square overflow-hidden"><img src="/images/ig-about-4.webp" alt="The Açai Club community" class="w-full h-full object-cover" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-dark">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-12 text-center">
        The Manifest
      </h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-dark border border-dark-border flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-charcoal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.75v.01M12 6.75c0-1.5 1-3 2.5-3.75M12 6.75c0-1.5-1-3-2.5-3.75M5.25 12a6.75 6.75 0 1113.5 0 6.75 6.75 0 01-13.5 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Never Blended</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">We serve 140g of pure açai, never blended down with banana or syrup. That's how almost nobody else does it & we never will.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-dark border border-dark-border flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-charcoal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"/><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Real Ingredients</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">No shortcuts on toppings either. Every adaptogen, granola & protein has been sourced for quality, regardless of cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-dark border border-dark-border flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-charcoal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Wellness</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">Built around wellness & an active lifestyle, not just a menu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-dark-card rounded-2xl p-8 border border-dark-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-dark border border-dark-border flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-charcoal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-normal text-light mb-3">Community First</h3>
          <p class="text-grey text-sm">From in-store vibes to weekend gatherings, everything we do is about bringing people together.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Press -->
  <section id="press" class="py-24 bg-dark-surface border-t border-dark-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-light mb-4">
        Press & Media
      </h2>
      <p class="text-grey text-lg">
        Get in touch at <a href="mailto:hello@theacaiclub.com" class="text-charcoal hover:underline">hello@theacaiclub.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
